<br>
Whatever you do - don't camp AC in OOT.<br>
<br>
I spent 60 hours on this camp first of all - and it was hard - even at 51, takes about 80% of mana (my int is 203 and I have +400 mana from items or so).  You can only get about 60% of mana in 6 minutes too.  Believe me - don't even try it.<br>
<br>
Eledaar Darkpyre,<br>
