<br>
I tried many of the methods described on this site, killing the mobs on the list of rares, etc...   The one that worked for me was leaving &quot;A  Drybone Bone&quot;  in the tower, til 7pm game time.     I killed that, then went around the desert looking for mummies.  Killed 2 shriveled mummies and 2 Dune Spiders and wham, there he was.  <br>
<br>
